imdb.plot outline: "Total Access" takes Radio Disney and Disney Channel audiences behind-the-scenes into the lives of their favorite artists including Dove Cameron, Zendaya, Bella Thorne, Selena Gomez, Demi Lovato, and Bridgit Mendler. Audiences are granted exclusive access to the creative process of recording music, filming a music video, going on tour and engaging fans. Exclusive video from Total Access interviews is available at RadioDisney.com.
